&lt;p&gt;When your script is imported with &lt;code&gt;Import-Module&lt;/code&gt;, the &lt;code&gt;.psm1&lt;/code&gt; script at the root of the module is sourced, executing the code within. In this case, that code is iterating over the &lt;code&gt;Public/&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;Private/&lt;/code&gt; directories and sourcing &lt;code&gt;.ps1&lt;/code&gt; Powershell scripts.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>